Class ResultSetProcessorRowPerEventForge

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.espertech.esper.epl.core.resultset.rowperevent.ResultSetProcessorRowPerEventForge
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSetProcessorFactoryForge

    public class ResultSetProcessorRowPerEventForge
extends java.lang.Object
implements ResultSetProcessorFactoryForge
    Result set processor prototype for the case: aggregation functions used in the select clause, and no group-by, and not all of the properties in the select clause are under an aggregation function.
